{"tid":1913062,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日牛扒","createTime":"2020-03-06T13:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T22:38:35.000Z","uid":281492,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50e3c64880140fd2d693d380ac939b7ef57d1000","tid":1913062,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSGBE75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSGBE75.jpg&h=da4ee1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYysMN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYysMN7.jpg&h=cfc661e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"713d4f3cbc5d3acd742ba356ca86a837b6e0166c","tid":1913062,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以餵我"},{"pid":"19453a5353a713cb5ad416986d8362eace37eaf0","tid":1913062,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"iron steak?"},{"pid":"cd9b5af39247777f120d492cf977bc435841a15e","tid":1913062,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"合成肉黎?"},{"pid":"6e2a64bc875958abd5949b90abc7b2e8dad9dfbb","tid":1913062,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:40:57.000Z","msg":"睇落唔錯<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5b629f9a2f332de6254792ae4975484484156c3","tid":1913062,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19453a5353a713cb5ad416986d8362eace37eaf0","tid":1913062,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"iron steak?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"is"},{"pid":"d6a5be9c4a3b772ff07a2cecb9b7d6da34fcfb44","tid":1913062,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"713d4f3cbc5d3acd742ba356ca86a837b6e0166c","tid":1913062,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以餵我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"首先你要行過嚟黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84213e41315c7197780bfe0a0ca770a15df96a22","tid":1913062,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd9b5af39247777f120d492cf977bc435841a15e","tid":1913062,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"合成肉黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"非"},{"pid":"665857ed1ff2caf88c975739d3d2a51cbc5cbe50","tid":1913062,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"很好"},{"pid":"f17fbd97b36d943d7e7879ba4ba16b40d71f1a6e","tid":1913062,"uid":209027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"三成先正"},{"pid":"abd019716948493bcc8c07582df6955b8c63f386","tid":1913062,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit